	<text>
		<body xml:lang="en">
			<div>

	<pb n="0001" facs="liv_000973_0001"/><!--pb/@n='6r'-->
<lb/><p rend="right"><placeName>57 Sloane St</placeName></p>
<lb/><p rend="right">22<hi rend="underline"><hi rend="sup">d</hi></hi> March</p>
<lb/><p>My Dear <persName>M<hi rend="underline"><hi rend="sup">r</hi></hi> Murray</persName></p>
<lb/><p>Enclosed you 
<lb/>will see an example 
<lb/>of Routledgism on 
<lb/>a grand scale which 
<lb/>I got from my brother 
<lb/>this morning. <choice><reg>T</reg><orig>t</orig></choice>hat's 
<lb/>going the "whole hog" 
<lb/>and no mistake 
<lb/>I want it back 
<lb/>as a curiosity 

	<pb n="0002" facs="liv_000973_0002"/><!--pb/@n='6v'--> 
<lb/><persName>J.P. Jewett</persName><add place="above">of Boston</add> &amp;c the 
<lb/>publisher of "Uncle Tom's 
<lb/>Cabin" is anxious 
<lb/>to get the book for 
<lb/>the somewhat 
<lb/>slippery looking thing 
<lb/>"Ten per cent in the 
<lb/>retail price of all 
<lb/>they sell" he says 
<lb/>this is the customary 
<lb/>rate among publishers 
<lb/>there. <persName>Jewett</persName> seems 
<lb/>an honourable man 
<lb/>as he refused to 

	<pb n="0003" facs="liv_000973_0003"/><!--pb/@n='7r'--> 
<lb/>publish a pro slavery 
<lb/>work by a <persName>D. D.</persName>
<lb/>whose other works 
<lb/>he had already published<reg>.</reg></p>
<lb/><p>You of course 
<lb/>understand the whole 
<lb/>matter better than 
<lb/>I do. I merely let 
<lb/>you know what 
<lb/>my brother<reg>'</reg>s letter 
<lb/>contains<reg>.</reg></p>
<lb/><p><persName>D<hi rend="sup"><hi rend="underline">r</hi></hi> Smith<reg>'</reg>s</persName> book 
<lb/>is splendidly bound 
<lb/>I am glad to have 

	<pb n="0004" facs="liv_000973_0004"/><!--pb/@n='7v'--> 
<lb/>it by me in this form<reg>.</reg>
<lb/>It is a magnificent 
<lb/>present. I would 
<lb/>have given my 
<lb/>ears to have had 
<lb/>it by me in <placeName>Africa</placeName><reg>.</reg></p>
<lb/><p>Believe me &amp;c</p>
<lb/><p><persName>David Livingstone</persName></p>
<lb/><p>My brother saw my 
<lb/>letter to the Times 
<lb/>in <placeName>America</placeName>. <choice><reg>T</reg><orig>t</orig></choice>hat 
<lb/>against <persName>Routledge</persName><reg>.</reg></p>
			
</div>
